// Generated by claude-setup-agentic-delivery-os (gen-opencode-config).
// Hybrid runtime: local Gemma via Ollama + cloud for high-stakes agents.
// baseURL targets the Docker host gateway; for host-only runs regenerate
// with --ollama-url http://localhost:11434/v1.
// Local agents need a TOOL-CAPABLE model (gemma3:1b cannot tool-call).
